en_132204_0	Showers or thundershowers will occur at several places over most provinces except Northern and Eastern provinces, after 2.00 pm, the Department of Meteorology said.
en_132204_1	It added that showers or thundershowers may occur at few places in Northern and Eastern provinces after 04.00 p.m.
en_132204_2	Few showers may occur in the Western and Southern coastal area in the morning.
en_132204_3	Fairly heavy falls (above 50mm) are also likely at some places.
en_132204_4	According to the MET department there may be temporary localized strong winds during thundershowers.
en_132204_5	General public is kindly requested to take adequate precautions to minimize damages caused by lightning activity.
